@84   = ~Balduran's Artifacts for the Merchants' League

Mendas wants the artifacts from the shipwreck for science, while claiming that the Merchants' League only wants to profit from them. Maybe I should hear for myself what the Merchants' League thinks of the whole thing? I'm sure I can come to an agreement with Aldeth that will satisfy us both.~
@85   = ~Balduran's Artifacts for the Merchants' League~
@86   = ~Balduran's Artifacts for the Merchants' League

I told Aldeth that I do not have any more items I am willing to sell him.~
@87   = ~Balduran's Artifacts for the Merchants' League

I sold Aldeth all of Balduran's possessions I found at the shipwreck site.~
@88   = ~Balduran's Artifacts for the Merchants' League

I sold Aldeth the logbook of Balduran.~
@89   = ~Balduran's Artifacts for the Merchants' League

I sold Aldeth Balduran's butterknife.~
@90   = ~Balduran's Artifacts for the Merchants' League

I sold Aldeth Balduran's golden sword.~
